  "title": "Doesn’t Need Experience - Sales and Marketing",
  "description": "<p>John sent out dozens of resumes after graduation and barely heard back.<br />Every company wanted experience - except one.</p><p>He joined a Sales & Marketing team with <strong>zero experience</strong>.<br />With training and effort, he picked up confidence, communication skills, and started earning based on performance.</p><p>Now, we’re looking for <strong>fresh grads and entry-level candidates</strong> who are ready to learn and grow.</p><p><strong>What you’ll do:</strong><br />• Execute on-ground sales & marketing campaigns<br />• Engage customers and represent established brands<br />• Learn communication and people skills on the job<br />• Work closely with a supportive team</p><p>✔ No experience required<br />✔ Training provided<br />✔ Career progression available</p><p>Start where you are. Grow as you go. <strong>Apply now</strong></p>",
